{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we automate the registration of new services.",
    "Initially, we search the service repository using the service name identified in Step 1-2 to determine whether the service is existing or new.",
    "Registration in the service repository is performed only if the service is identified as new.",
    "The service description, which is a mandatory item in the service data model, is generated by providing the 6W1H needs as input to the LLM.",
    "This enables the registration of new services in the service repository."
  ]
}